365
00:20:36,835 --> 00:20:39,963
- Sorry I didn't blow the game.
- No. You did the right thing...

366
00:20:40,072 --> 00:20:42,632
and you finally got Dad
to one of your ball games.

367
00:20:42,741 --> 00:20:45,369
- Screw him.
- Yeah.

368
00:20:45,477 --> 00:20:49,140
I miss him so much.

369
00:20:49,248 --> 00:20:52,012
<i>On the next</i>
Arrested Development.

370
00:20:52,117 --> 00:20:55,314
- <i>Maeby gets her father a job.</i>
- I gotta fire one of ya.

371
00:20:55,420 --> 00:20:58,116
<i>Andy Richter! Here are those head shots</i>
